CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. It identifies an individual signer for a (non-US) entity who can (and will certify that they can) sign Forms W-8 on behalf of the entity.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Identifies an individual signer for a (non-US) entity who can (and will certify that they can) sign Forms W-8 on behalf of the entity.
CustomField.label: Form W8 Signer Indicator
